metadata.name: Magical Garden
metadata.description: Special selection of the most popular photographs from lost "Frens Editions" collection by photographer KireevArt. Only the best restored works of this beloved collection are included here. Open edition for all art lovers will introduce authentic fairy tale style and visual language of KireevArt, which is a unique art code to the world of this rare art photography. Own artist vision, sublimated into wonderful digital images. Join fine art and enjoy the Journey.
